is all good,but lots of class can provide dmg to some point as well as other nice abilities. A mage can do decent dmg, but can also CoH peoples around etc.<br>
<br>
To make us more group profitable, wed need to have buffs or something. Well they simply need to change how the coding of one simple line of spells we have.<br>
<br>
The Okeils line of spells should not be a dmg shield, but a dmg add-on.<br>
<br>
You see more and more weapons that are now, lets say, 10dmg 20dly AND with something called: <br>
+1 fire dmg.<br>
<br>
